<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>In the field of academics, students have many technical things. At schools and colleges too, there are interactive boards equipped in all the classrooms to view animated video for the chapter of the syllabus. Before starting the chapter or module the students can view the summary or video clip for that chapter in the smart board and then start with the detail of the chapter. There are many quizzes also for the students to solve after completion of the chapter.</p>
